The subtle edge

Faith isn’t “believe no matter what.”
It’s closer to:

commit → act → measure → refine → recommit

That loop keeps you honest and moving.

⸻

Guardrail so it stays clean

Keep two channels separate:

* Narrative (fuel): vision, momentum, belief
* Measurement (steering): results, errors, deltas

Let the narrative drive effort, but let measurement decide direction.

